<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بُنَيَّ إِنَّ البِرَّ شَيْءٌ هَيِّنْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المَنْطِقُ اللَّيِّنُ والطُّعَيِّمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">ومثله:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قَالَتْ سُلَيْمَى لَا أُحِبُّ الجَعْدِيْنْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلَا القِصَارَ إِنَّهُمْ مَنَاتِينْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>يَا رُبَّ جَعْدٍ فِيهِمْ لَوْ تَدْرِينْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يَضْرِبُ قَبْلَ السَّبِطِ المَقَادِيمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">ومثله:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>يَطْعَنُهَا بِخِنْجَرٍ مِنْ لَحْمِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عِنْدَ الذُّنَابَى فِي مَكَانٍ سُخْنِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قال الفراء:</span> أنشدني أبو الجرَّاحِ:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>واللهِ مَا فَضْلِي عَلَى الجِيرَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>إِلَّا عَلَى الأَخْوَالِ والأَعْمَامِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>